summary:
I am fascinated by all kinds of machines, systems and communication methods. Learning new technology and delving deeper into the ones I already know allows me to create functional applications helping people and business. 

Not interested in the gambling or firearms business opportunity.

Doing a BA in Graphic Design taught me to break down problems, structure information, appreciate graphical language and work in a team. The last three years, I have become experienced in simple page applications, full-stack projects and have worked with various clients to create portfolio, e-commerce and interactive online works to life. My 10 month stint as a Junior Programming Teacher taught me to communicate with the students and deeply understand problems while finding elegant solutions to them.
